channel.title: Dds-speced / Delta client
channel.description:
I've been looking for a client with veng for dds-speced for a few days straight now and couldn't find it. I did found some Delta clients but everytime I try to log in with the, they automatically log out. So I need a Delta client that'll work with DDS-Speced. I do have 1 client but it doesn't have veng.
If anyone can give me, I'll appreciate it.
Thanks in advance, Me.
